-- Etihad, Air France-KLM to Announce Code-Share Agreement, FT Says
-- B y   J i m   S i l v e r
-- 2012-10-07T22:55:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-07/etihad-air-france-klm-to-announce-code-share-agreement-ft-says.html
Agreement to be announced today, FT
says, citing two unidentified people familiar with plan.
* Deal doesn’t involve equity stakes, FT says
* Air Berlin, in which Etihad bought 29.2% stake in Dec., will
also announce code-sharing agreement with Air France today: FT
* Etihad,  Air France-KLM (AF)  declined to comment on either
agreement, Air Berlin couldn’t be reached: FT  To contact the reporter on this story:
